<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-nuclear-police-authority> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Civil Nuclear Police Authority oversees the Civil Nuclear Constabulary (CNC) and must ensure that their policing meets the need of the nuclear operating companies. CNPA is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero ."@en .
